VThe other method of extraction is what's called the in situ.
p119
aVAnd here, massive amounts of water
p120
aVare superheated and pumped through the ground,
p121
aVthrough these vasts networks of pipelines,
p122
aVseismic lines, drill paths, compressor stations.
