aa(lp132
VThe oil produced from either method
p133
aVproduces more greenhouse gas emissions than any other oil.
p134
aVThis is one of the reasons why it's called the world's dirtiest oil.
p135
aVIt's also one of the reasons
p136
aVwhy it is the largest and fastest-growing single source of carbon in Canada,
