aVOil sands \u2014 or rather, I should say tar sands \u2014
p141
aVoil sands is a PR-created term
p142
aVso that the oil companies wouldn't be trying to promote something
p143
aVthat sounds like a sticky tar-like substance that's the world's dirtiest oil.
p144
aVSo they decided to call it oil sands.
